Title: The City of the Dead
Description:
An ancient city of the dead can only mean one thing. The Veiled Ossuary off the coast of northern Thaldraszus.

It's extensive, remote, and hard to approach. The perfect place to hide something. I'm not sure what we'll find there, $n. But you can bet that it won't appreciate our presence.
ObjectivesText: Meet up with Naleidea at the Veiled Ossuary in Thaldraszus.
